EN: Their company's website has a high traffic volume, with thousands of visits every day.

ZH: 我正在寻找一家提供无限流量的手机运营商。
EN: I am looking for a mobile service provider that offers unlimited data.

ZH: 他在网上购物时注意流量的消耗，避免超出预算。
EN: He pays attention to the data usage when shopping online to avoid exceeding the budget.

ZH: 这个视频流量很大，需要一些时间来加载。
EN: This video has a large data size and may take some time to load.

